Ace singer Innocent Idibia aka Tu Face has visited the burial site of late singer Olanrewaju Abdul-Ganiu Fasai aka Sound Sultan with some people. Sound Sultan died in July 2021 of complications from cancer. Tu face, who was known as one of his closest buddies, took a step in paying tribute to him.   Singer Olamide makes U-turn, gifts berated fan car     Chimamanda Adichie recalls last moments with mom     Seven Nigerian musicians who rose to fame from slums   In the video he shared, the ace singer presented a bouquet of flowers around the grave while playing background music featuring Tu Face and Sound Sultan. The gentlemen were in a sad emotional state as they dropped their bouquets and bid farewell to the deceased.